    • Constructor Detail

      • OCSPPreferencesImpl

        public OCSPPreferencesImpl()
        Sets the defaults. The defaults are :
        - Check revocation information if available
        - use locally configured ocsp server if no aia present
        - do not sign the request
        - maxClockSkew time = 5
        - responseFreshness allowed = 52600 (1 year)
